translation.Name: Greece Note Static
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_1: Checkpoint Zeta, this is Checkpoint Epsilon, Radio check, over.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_3: Checkpoint Epsilon, this is Checkpoint Zeta, I read you 5 by 5, over.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_5: We are unable to secure a signal with Command. Can you establish a connection? over.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_7: Copy that Checkpoint Zeta, Wait, over.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_9: Checkpoint Epsilon, this is Checkpoint Zeta, do you copy? over.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_11: Checkpoint Zeta, this is Checkpoint Epsilon, we hear you. Could a connection be made? over.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_13: Negatory. Nothing but static. I don't know what is happening but I have a bad feeling about this, over.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_15: Roger that Zeta. Maintain previous orders, but call in on 30 minute intervals. No infected are to enter this city. We may be on our own now. Over.
